OL,5, A burst water pipe that cut supply off 
OL,6, on Christmas Day has left some         
OL,7, residents with "brown" water, they have
OL,8, claimed.                               
OL,10,FAround 3,000 residents in parts of     
OL,11,FSouth Gloucestershire were without     
OL,12,Fwater yesterday after the burst stopped
OL,13,Fwater supply and caused "very poor"    
OL,14,Fpressure.                              
OL,16,FOne woman said their Christmas dinner  
OL,17,Fwas "ruined".                          
OL,19,FBristol Water said people should leave 
OL,20,Ftaps running to clear discolouration.  
